<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include("../components/_head.ejs", { title: "sky coffee", filename: "cafe" }) %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="p-header">
      <h1>
        <a href="/cafe">
          <img src="/assets/images/cafe/logo.svg" alt="sky coffee" />
        </a>
      </h1>
    </header>
    <main>
      <section>
        <div class="p-hero">
          <img
            class="p-hero__image p-hero__image--sp"
            src="/assets/images/cafe/sp_main-visual.png"
            srcset="
              /assets/images/cafe/sp_main-visual.png    1x,
              /assets/images/cafe/sp_main-visual@2x.png 2x
            "
            alt="複数の青いカップのコーヒー"
          />
          <img
            class="p-hero__image p-hero__image--pc"
            src="/assets/images/cafe/pc_main-visual.png"
            srcset="
              /assets/images/cafe/pc_main-visual.png    1x,
              /assets/images/cafe/pc_main-visual@2x.png 2x
            "
            alt="複数の青いカップのコーヒー"
          />
        </div>
      </section>
      <nav>
        <div class="container">
          <ul class="p-nav">
            <li class="p-nav__item"><a href="#">manu</a></li>
            <li class="p-nav__item"><a href="#">blog</a></li>
            <li class="p-nav__item"><a href="#">access</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </nav>
      <section class="p-concept">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="p-concept__visual">
            <img
              class="p-concept__visual-image"
              src="/assets/images/cafe/concept.png"
              alt="爽やかなカフェのカップ"
              srcset="/assets/images/cafe/concept.png 1x, /assets/images/cafe/concept@2x.png 2x"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="p-concept__content">
            <p class="p-concept__subtitle">Concept</p>
            <h2 class="p-concept__title">心静かにコーヒーを</h2>
            <p class="p-concept__text">
              立ち止まって、<br />空の青さを眺めて、<br />一息つきましょう
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="p-blog">
        <div class="container">
          <h2 class="c-section-title">blog</h2>
          <p class="c-section-subtitle">ブログ</p>
          <ul class="p-blog__list">
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="c-article">
                <article>
                  <div class="c-article__image-area">
                    <img
                      class="c-article__image"
                      src="/assets/images/cafe/thumbnail01.png"
                      alt="ブログのサムネイル"
                      srcset="
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail01.png    1x,
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail01@2x.png 2x
                      "
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="c-article__title">コーヒーカー始めました。</h4>
                  <p class="c-article__date">2030.08.08</p>
                </article>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="c-article">
                <article>
                  <div class="c-article__image-area">
                    <img
                      class="c-article__image"
                      src="/assets/images/cafe/thumbnail02.png"
                      alt="ブログのサムネイル"
                      srcset="
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail02.png    1x,
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail02@2x.png 2x
                      "
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="c-article__title">濃厚クリーミーなミルクをどうぞ</h4>
                  <p class="c-article__date">2030.08.05</p>
                </article>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="c-article">
                <article>
                  <div class="c-article__image-area">
                    <img
                      class="c-article__image"
                      src="/assets/images/cafe/thumbnail03.png"
                      alt="ブログのサムネイル"
                      srcset="
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail03.png    1x,
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail03@2x.png 2x
                      "
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="c-article__title">
                    Sky Coffeeのオリジナル曲が完成！無料ダウンロード可能です。
                  </h4>
                  <p class="c-article__date">2030.08.02</p>
                </article>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="c-article">
                <article>
                  <div class="c-article__image-area">
                    <img
                      class="c-article__image"
                      src="/assets/images/cafe/thumbnail04.png"
                      alt="ブログのサムネイル"
                      srcset="
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail04.png    1x,
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail04@2x.png 2x
                      "
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="c-article__title">ハイキング用のコーヒーを販売中です。</h4>
                  <p class="c-article__date">2030.07.28</p>
                </article>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="c-article">
                <article>
                  <div class="c-article__image-area">
                    <img
                      class="c-article__image"
                      src="/assets/images/cafe/thumbnail05.png"
                      alt="ブログのサムネイル"
                      srcset="
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail05.png    1x,
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail05@2x.png 2x
                      "
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="c-article__title">ショップの壁を塗ってみました。</h4>
                  <p class="c-article__date">2030.07.27</p>
                </article>
              </a>
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="#" class="c-article">
                <article>
                  <div class="c-article__image-area">
                    <img
                      class="c-article__image"
                      src="/assets/images/cafe/thumbnail06.png"
                      alt="ブログのサムネイル"
                      srcset="
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail06.png    1x,
                        /assets/images/cafe/thumbnail06@2x.png 2x
                      "
                    />
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="c-article__title">ブログをはじめました。</h4>
                  <p class="c-article__date">2030.07.26</p>
                </article>
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <button class="c-button">ブログ一覧</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <footer class="p-footer">
      <img class="p-footer__logo" src="/assets/images/cafe/logo-white.svg" alt="sky coffee" />
      <p class="p-footer__copywrite">©sky coffee</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
